  "body": "#### System information\n\nGeth version: `1.3.6`\nOS & Version: `4.4.0-12-generic #28-Ubuntu SMP Wed Mar 9 00:33:55 UTC 2016 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux` \nCommit hash : bf324bd24be9036046e36c6248b2d7c31cce9eca\n#### Expected behaviour\n\nA response according to the JSON-RPC examples: https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC\n#### Actual behaviour\n\n`curl: (52) Empty reply from server`\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\ngeth --rpcapi \"db,eth,net,web3,personal\"\n\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"web3_clientVersion\",\"params\":[],\"id\":1}' http://127.0.0.1:30303 \n\nAlso --rpcport doesn't seem to work either\n\nThis seems to be similar to what is reported in issue #1942\n",
