    "body": "You mean something like this?\n\n```\ngeth --rpc        # would start HTTP interface with the default api's\ngeth --rpc a,b    # would start the HTTP interface with a and b enabled\n```\n\nI don't think this is supported in the cli package since it's really hard to figure out how to parse. E.g. `geth --rpc console` would add console to the rpc api's instead of executing the console command. Maybe there are other packages that allow for this.\n",
